==English==

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/bɒnət/}}
* Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɒnɪt|-ɒnɪt]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A type of [[hat]], once worn by [[women]] or [[children]], held in place by [[ribbon]]s tied under the [[chin]].
# (''mostly British/Australian'') The [[hinge]]d [[cover]] over the [[engine]] of a [[motor car]].
# {{nautical}} A length of [[canvas]] attached to a [[fore-and-aft]] [[sail]] to increase the pulling power.

====Synonyms====
*(''cover over the engine of a motor car''): [[hood]] (''US'')

